1. What are two low-cost or no-cost ways to help keep customer service agents motivated?
Ans: C. Encourage replenishing breaks, and take time for team building.

2. Why is it important to tailor motivation to individual agents?
Ans: C. People are motivated for different reasons.

3. When would you use the Know, Feel, Do approach?
Ans: A. Before one-on-one meetings with employees
